               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18561027-name-747" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18561027-name-747" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18561027-name-747" type="surname" value="BOND"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18561027-name-747" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN BOND</persName>
                  </hi>. <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> When I found the prisoner at Peekham, he was at his brother's house—his furniture was still at Acorn-street—I had watched the house night and day, and had not seen him—I saw his wife on one occasion—he is a journeyman cooper.</p>
